{"tid":577084,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[WIN7色彩管理]相片檢視器睇相變色","createTime":"2018-03-01T12:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T14:29:02.000Z","uid":5375,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc83b7c286c45b977cdcb3047996e2d519446a5f","tid":577084,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"唔知有無巴打識WIN7色彩管理既野，是咁的，<br />\n我需要裝一個ICC設定檔，裝完無問題，但用相片檢視器睇相會變到好深對比度，上網SEARCH左好耐淨係搵到「相片檢視器底色變黃」呢個問題，但同我情況唔關事。我轉返預設ICC個問題就解決，但一裝返新ICC就唔得。其他畫面顏色無問題，係打開相片檢視器會變到勁深對比度。我用手機影左圖俾大家參考，THX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一張係預設ICC：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/193336_1f6a4cabe171485567197595306b7094.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F193336_1f6a4cabe171485567197595306b7094.jpg&h=c6aa49ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二張係新ICC正常相片檢視器情況，因為裝完新ICC唔關相既話會無事，所以我影到，但關左重開張相就會變左第三張圖咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/193346_afe768b406b31285ef65fc4f741266b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F193346_afe768b406b31285ef65fc4f741266b0.jpg&h=2888ac19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三張相，對比度變到勁深，但睇返FOLDER入面個預覽圖顏色係同第二張圖一樣，係開相片檢視器睇先會變左<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/193409_6d821a51aff597f33af3cdf77f363804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F193409_6d821a51aff597f33af3cdf77f363804.jpg&h=99b1714f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1665ae6223f1c9d042052717e4a2c69a790b5214","tid":577084,"uid":36478,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc1d5ba96d7f6b2d7a0b785fbf4e8c759f9b8c0","tid":577084,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1665ae6223f1c9d042052717e4a2c69a790b5214","tid":577084,"uid":36478,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T14:29:02.000Z","msg":"好撚醒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}